-- ============================================================
-- Master of Ghouls Rework: custom spell 200132, talent_dbc, spell_script_names
-- ============================================================
-- Redesign: Keeps 60s Raise Dead CD reduction. Ghoul is now a temporary guardian
-- (not a permanent pet). Raise Dead summons 3 additional guardian ghouls.
-- Army of the Dead raises twice as many undead.
--
-- Approach: Redirect talent 1984 from vanilla spell 52143 to custom spell 200132.
-- Core checks HasAura(52143) for the pet summon path; since the player now has
-- 200132 instead, core takes the guardian path naturally. Module C++ scripts
-- check for 200132 to add extra ghouls and double the army.
--
-- Custom spell IDs:
--   200132 = Master of Ghouls talent aura (clone of 52143)
--   200133 = Summon Extra Ghouls (based on 46585, SummonProps 713 for multi-summon)

-- 200132: Master of Ghouls (clone of 52143 with updated description)
